OL,3,CChichester Festival Theatre removes
OL,4,Cpork products from menu
OL,6,FChichester Festival Theatre has pulled
OL,7,Fthe sale of pork-based products from
OL,8,Fone of its menus, following pressure
OL,9,Ffrom animal welfare groups.
OL,11,FThe site is currently showing The
OL,12,FThree Little Pigs, and says it will
OL,13,Fnot be selling pork products at its
OL,14,FMinvera Bar, whilst the production is
OL,15,Fongoing.
OL,17,FIt follows pressure from animal
OL,18,Fwelfare group, PETA, who called on the
OL,19,Ftheatre back in February to remove the
OL,20,Fsale of pork during the showings.
