OL,3,CChichester Festival Theatre removes
OL,4,Cpork products from menu
OL,6,FThe theatre said it listened to
OL,7,Ffeedback from PETA and carefully
OL,8,Fconsidered how it could create a
OL,9,Fthoughtful and inclusive experience
OL,10,Ffor audiences.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the theatre said:
OL,13,F"We appreciate PETA's passion and
OL,14,Fadvocacy for animal welfare. As a
OL,15,Ftheatre committed to creating
OL,16,Fthoughtful and inclusive experiences
OL,17,Ffor all audiences, we have taken their
OL,18,Ffeedback into careful consideration.
