OL,3,CChichester Festival Theatre removes
OL,4,Cpork products from menu
OL,6,F"For the duration of the run of The
OL,7,FThree Little Pigs, we will be removing
OL,8,Fpork products from the special daytime
OL,9,Ffamily menu which will be available
OL,10,Ffor this production in the Minerva
OL,11,FBar, which is the primary catering
OL,12,Fspace used by audiences attending this
OL,13,Fshow. We offer vegetarian and vegan
OL,14,Foptions in our restaurant and cafes to
OL,15,Fensure that plant-based choices are
OL,16,Fclearly available and accessible to
OL,17,Fall visitors.
