OL,3,CChichester Festival Theatre removes
OL,4,Cpork products from menu
OL,6,FIn a statement on PETA's website, the
OL,7,Forganisation welcomed the decision,
OL,8,Fsaying: "The Chichester Festival
OL,9,FTheatre has made the compassionate
OL,10,Ffirst step to stop serving the flesh
OL,11,Fof pigs ` who, just like those in the
OL,12,Fshow, experience close family bonds
OL,13,Fand have a desire to live free from
OL,14,Fharm ` at the Minerva Bar.
OL,16,F"We are now calling on them to also
OL,17,Fremove the 'pigs in blankets' and
OL,18,Fother pig products from the theatre's
OL,19,FBrasserie restaurant and urge diners
OL,20,Fto show kindness to all animals by
OL,21,Falways picking the vegan option."
